message.entry: Configuring the global fimath from MATLAB preference is not recommended. Do not save global fimath as a MATLAB preference. Use 'removeglobalfimathpref' to remove a non-factory default setting global fimath from MATLAB preferences. See Release Notes and documentation for details.
Invalid call to dummy fimath constructor. Please report this problem \nto support@mathworks.com, including sample code that reproduces the error.
Word length must be scalar integer.
The fimath dictionary does not contain a fimath with the tag: {0}.
Invalid SlopeAdjustmentFactor specified; the SlopeAdjustmentFactor must be greater than or equal to 1 and less than 2.
The fimath dictionary already contains a fimath with the tag: {0}.
Function ''{0}'' is not supported for code generation.
This parameter must be a fimath.
{0} on fimath object is not defined.

You cannot save global fimath as a MATLAB preference. Use 'removeglobalfimathpref' to remove the non-factory default global fimath from your MATLAB preferences. See Release Notes and documentation for details.
